  <summary date="2015-03-26T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Vulnerable Immigrant Voice Act 

Amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to require that counsel at the government's expense in a removal or related appeal proceeding shall be provided only for an alien who is: (1) an unaccompanied child, or (2) unable to represent himself or herself due to a serious mental disability.</summary>
